Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是罗伊·马斯坦古吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰之链金术师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么年轻就被提拔 到底使了什么内部关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升得越快的人 摔得自然也快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:01:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是罗伊·马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大总统阁下出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去南部视察了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南部？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有股讨厌的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却很让人怀旧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来视察一下 居然发现一个不得了的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}躲藏在地下的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲锋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼加主妇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真赞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 战斗的话 我有点不占光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然逃跑 卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地…呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马黛儿 你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 罗亚也不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 事情稍微变得有点麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要准备逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可让人头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:03:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金格·布拉德雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家的最高领袖找我有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你几岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今年就60岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪大了 身体就没法自由活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把这工作快点完成 舒服地回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就引退吧 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂 这么厉害的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我阿姆斯壮家代代相传的雕像术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就用全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是这么个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经保护了少年和妇人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就只管消灭怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是大总统的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没这么心潮澎湃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是阿姆斯壮阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也参加了伊修瓦尔歼灭战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原先的同志吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更应该避免这次战斗了 我不喜欢无谓的杀生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想把我们全杀光？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 没有你那最强之盾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有能贯穿一切的最强之矛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的我 是如何在枪林弹雨的战场活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立下战功 得到现在的地位的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你有最强之盾一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拥有最强之眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再杀几次你才会死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太暗了 什么也看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快打开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就死了15次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有几次呢 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然大总统亲自出马吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以夹着尾巴逃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想这么干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是狗的忠诚心太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮她逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗亚 多鲁契德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别妨碍我 快打开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没时间和你在这里耗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫打开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快打开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我在这里看着伙伴被干掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把你放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们俩拜托我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多鲁契德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能…出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 布拉德雷先生哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的部下弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对棋子产生感情了吗 真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡扯 你以为我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是强欲的古利德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金钱 女人 部下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切都是我的所有物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不会丢弃我的所有物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为欲望太深了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强欲 越来越无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在那躺一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是爱德华的弟弟吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 马黛儿小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马黛儿小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔 喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是哥哥 全身都是血
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅自打开把她拉出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是阿尔的错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识这里的幕后黑手 古利德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问出重要的情报了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有对军队有利的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会了 不是为了军队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你和他们有交易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和加害军队中枢的家伙们联手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你那钢制的手臂与你弟弟的铠甲之身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是老实人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收队了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好珍惜你的弟弟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱力克兄弟的事情 多谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护国家链金术师的生命也是军队的任务之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 也让军队来保护你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我做国家链金术师？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见 我是个病弱的主妇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这样微薄之力也要借用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家还不至于如此紧迫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是严厉的批判
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时 说不定您就改变主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德那家伙 手上有咬尾蛇的刺青
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬尾蛇？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 休斯中佐也说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和贤者之石相关的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯阁下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华·爱力克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我的身体被带去那边的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 对于人体链成还是不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是没进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不全是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大总统之前说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队内部有不稳定的因素
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和贤者之石以及咬尾蛇刺青的人们有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想抓住他们的尾巴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德也有着咬尾蛇的刺青
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为什么有必要全杀光？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想抓住他们的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住之后审问就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就为了对付这么点人 大总统亲自出马也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 都是些无法解释的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时跟着军队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南部的视察如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢之链金术师的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定连他们的师傅也是人柱的人材
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 另一个意外的收获
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个世纪前离开这里的某张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床了 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 大伙聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作自受 最强之盾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你依然是个不错的女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强的矛 色欲的拉斯多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴食的库拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一点都没瘦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒的恩维 你的兴趣还是如此诡异
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怠惰的斯洛斯去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前就一直偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:17:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还在干活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都和一百年前没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这家伙是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒的拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是金格·布拉德雷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 作为金格·布拉德雷这个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人为了最后的结局而准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的新兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会衰老的人造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上没什么不可能的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是你的口头禅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老年痴呆了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼神真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你的本性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低级货 恩维
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所愿 把你捏碎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个还不住手？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在我这父亲面前做这种丑恶的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不见还真是老了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分享了我灵魂的儿子哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么背叛了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该是老爸最清楚的 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强欲的古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么生的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就怎么活着罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法满足我的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会为我工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 恶劣的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水温正好 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱的业火可没有这么温和吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什么样的东西 我先去看了 兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到出生的地方 我的灵魂中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃坏肚子我可不管 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了即将来临的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你们致死不虞的忠诚和安宁祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 杰利姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视察如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常充实的视察
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 你也一大把年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把位子让给后辈 放松一下就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我的身体还很结实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我在南边遇到了钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小小的链金术师？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:21:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰利姆真的是很喜欢爱德华的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 最年少的国家链金术师不是很帅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 我也想学链金术
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学那种东西做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得国家资格 为爸爸做点事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 将来让杰利姆来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异邦人投出的小石子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成波纹 产生连锁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.38,0:24:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于做出了巨大的漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.58,0:24:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是那个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.36,0:24:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十五话 东方的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.47,0:24:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等 笑里藏刀 窥探贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.24,0:00:03.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}不必消去这份记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}人生不是还很漫长？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:08.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}那些没有做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:12.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}只是想重新做起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:28.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}明明一直在追赶着梦的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:35.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}跌跌撞撞地走在弯曲的小道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:38.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不奢望回到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.34,0:00:41.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只是在苦寻那片丢失的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:43.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}就像你明白一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:48.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}除去那像牺牲之后的悲伤表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:50.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}罪孽之后并不是泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:52.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}而是一直以来背负的苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:53.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}迷失在没有出口的情感迷宫中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:55.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在等待着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:57.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}就像在白色笔记本上刻画一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:00:58.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}很想诚实地说出心声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:00.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在逃避什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.65,0:01:02.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}…原来是叫做现实的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:05.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}为了实现愿望而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.61,0:01:09.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不禁想要大喊  你能听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}平安无事却让人没法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:15.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}…无家可归
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:19.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}感谢同伴们带来的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:21.67,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}所以要更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:24.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:27.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}这种痛苦也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:33.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\blur4}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:38.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:44.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}约定和契约  被初夏的微风所怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:48.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}两个人互相依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:57.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在强颜欢笑的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.88,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}隐藏着逐渐扩大的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:12.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}所以  只装做没有发现  选择了重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.77,0:23:21.67,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}在桌边继续等待那没有震撼的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:30.06,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在空白的夜里  无法迎接的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:34.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}其实我全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:40.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}那天看到的绯红天空
